name: namoridane
description: Trained with 768x768 img on Nai. based on namoridane on ig. img generated with anyv3 and nai. lora kinda struggles with hands, youll understand why when checking reference imgs from ig. Struggles with simple background prompt too. v2 and 2.1 seems to do better for white bg. Did some more testing, lora kinda hit or miss lol. Added dataset for anyone who wants to train lora themselves
